---
title: Spanakopita-Inspired Chicken Tenders and Flatbreads with Marinated Tomatoes
description: Spanakopita is a savoury Greek pie made of phyllo dough, spinach and cheese. Tonight, we've swapped the phyllo for flatbread to make "spanakopizza." Creamy ricotta, tangy feta, spinach, chicken tenders and our Dill-Garlic Spice Blend unite to bring you a bit of Mediterranean flavour joy in every bite!
